/p>]]>; </description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p> Trevor Rainbolt <a href="https://flowingdata.com/2023/03/14/finding-the-physical-location-in-an-online-video-via-google-maps-clues/">非常擅长根据 Google 街景中的单个帧对地点进行地理定位</a>。他过去只在办公桌上直播，但现在他正在探索物理世界。 <a href="https://www.nytimes.com/2024/06/19/magazine/trevor-rainbolt-geoguessr-google-maps.html?unlocked_article_code=1.200.zUNN.jXIx4MadUkh6&#038;smid=url-share">托马斯·韦伯 (Tomas Weber) 为《纽约时报》介绍了 Rainbolt 的扩展观点</a>。</p><blockquote><p> 《Rainbolt》最平庸的时刻现在带有一点顿悟和认可的酊剂。事实证明，如果你在电脑上着迷于它的质地和色调，那么第一次触摸泰国草会更加激动人心：这是与一位长期记者面对面会面的兴奋，是与一位资深记者的第一次约会。老暗恋。 Rainbolt 利用互联网的制图技术来增强世界的强度，将虚拟与现实融合在一起，使两者都更加令人愉悦。去年七月，他在一段视频中宣布，他很快就会登上乞力马扎罗山，他说：“如果有山，抑郁症就不可能是真的。”他的路线：谷歌街景相机十年前攀登的路线。</p></blockquote><p>数据为旅程提供信息。</p><p>另请参阅：<a href="https://flowingdata.com/2011/11/24/touching-google-streetview-stop-motion/">地址近似</a>，定格动画冒险。</p><p><strong>标签：</strong><a href="https://flowingdata.com/tag/google-streetview/" rel="tag">谷歌街景</a>,<a href="https://flowingdata.com/tag/new-york-times/" rel="tag">纽约时报</a>,<a href="https://flowingdata.com/tag/trevor-rainbolt/" rel="tag">特雷弗·雷恩博尔特</a></p>]]>;</content:encoded><post-id xmlns="com-wordpress:feed-additions:1"> 74531</post-id></item><item><title>流动数据 17</title><link/> https://flowingdata.com/2024/07/02/flowingdata-at-17/<dc:creator><![CDATA[Nathan Yau]]></dc:creator><pubDate> Tue, 02 Jul 2024 14:23:48 +0000</pubDate> <category><![CDATA[Site News]]></category><category><![CDATA[birthday]]></category><guid ispermalink="false"> https://flowingdata.com/?p=74552 </guid><description><![CDATA[<p> <a href="https://flowingdata.com/2024/07/02/flowingdata-at-17/"><img width="750" height="438" src="https://i0.wp.com/flowingdata.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/keep-on-going.jpg?fit=750%2C438&amp;quality=89&amp;ssl=1" class="attachment-medium size-medium wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/flowingdata.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/keep-on-going.jpg?w=822&amp;quality=89&amp;ssl=1 822w, https://i0.wp